briefdescription.para: Convert Table Registry Entry for a Table into a Message.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Extracts the Table Registry information for the table specified by the CFE_TBL_TaskData_t::HkTlmTblRegIndex variable. It then formats the Registry contents into a format appropriate for downlink.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: CFE_TBL_TaskData_t::HkTlmTblRegIndex is assumed to be a valid index into the Table Registry.

briefdescription.para: Aborts load by freeing associated inactive buffers and sending event message.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This function aborts the load for the table whose registry entry is identified by the registry record pointer given as an argument. Aborting the load consists of freeing any associated inactive buffer and issuing an event message.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: The given registry record pointer is assumed to be valid.

parameterdescription.para: Pointer to registry record entry for the table whose load is to be aborted
